                              <p><sic>Avertisement</sic> subject to any <sic>correcture</sic> in
                                                  <sic>stile</sic> you consider just</p>
                              <p>To the friends and adherents of our Religion</p>
                              <p rend="align(right)"><placeName>St Louis, Mo</placeName>
                                        <date>August 5612</date>.</p>
                              <p>The Jewish Congregation ,,Bne Brith” in this city, desirous to
                                        erect<lb/> a house of worship, have bought a lot in the
                                        southern part of the city (in <placeName>Jackson
                                                  Str</placeName>) and also a place where to
                                                  <sic>burry</sic> their dead.</p>
                              <p>Though this congregation has been formed only 3 years ago and<lb/>
                                        consists of only 30 young Israelites lately immigrated to
                                        this country<lb/> and yet struggling with the
                                                  <del>foundation</del> origin of their material
                                        existence,<lb/> they have now already paid for both without
                                        asking the aid of older<lb/> and wealthier communities; but
                                        to erect a suitable building, though<lb/> not a very costly
                                        one, with all the simplicity that only our Religion<lb/>
                                        approves, exceeds our very limited means, and we call
                                        therefore upon<lb/> the Thousands of Israelites now in
                                                  <placeName>America</placeName>, as Individuals or
                                        in Congregations associated to contribute their mite for
                                        this holy purpose<lb/> with <add>?</add> is known to be a
                                        prospering growing city, and we hope to grow with it;<lb/> a
                                                  <add>?</add> heartfelt thanks would we pay then to
                                        other congregations<lb/> but <add>?</add> any donations
                                                  <add>?</add> any sum lent without interest but to
                                        be paid back within three years, will be thankfully
                                        received<lb/> and <sic>receited</sic> for by * _ _ _ _ _</p>
                              <p>or if sent by Post to <persName role="author"><hi rend="underline"
                                                  >Isidor Bush</hi></persName></p>
                              <p rend="indent(3)">President of K. K. ,,Bne Brith” <add>?</add></p>
                              <p><persName>L Schwarzkopf</persName> Secret.<del>ary</del>
                                                    <persName>N Taussig</persName> V. P.</p>
                              <p>* In the Occident you will please fill this blank by:</p>
                              <p>  <hi rend="underline">the Editor of this paper</hi></p>
                              <p>in the extra prints on letter paper you will leave this blank</p>
